      "date": "2015-02-15 19:35:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAlex: each of the per-layer lct_exit() methods appears to be able to block very shortly due to some others spin-locks used to protect linked-list management, but with no dead-lock possible scenario.",
