      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAlex: Sorry to have been unclear, but the fact that none of the ->lct_exit() methods can end-up in a schedule was already implicit in my previous answer, since I only checked that the only possible stalls some of them can imply are during other spin-locks but with no possible dead-lock.",
